{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But previous days, we already saw some movements-- the Germans starting to get out of the camp, you know, and cars moving left and right.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we thought there's something happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I must say that everybody was look at me where I was a strong guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest of them couldn't even stand up on their leg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least I could stand up on my leg and walk, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Most of the people were so weak already they couldn't even walk, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they started to go to the bathroom, you know, on the way there, you know-- just happened to pass away or die while, you know, they couldn't stand on their leg.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was a camp in the latest month, you know, when the Germans already can see, you know, that that's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They really didn't bother too much with us already, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The food was getting less and less, and it was the start of the bad situation in the last months of the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A French jeep arrived, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the time we saw the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But maybe two, three hours before, we didn't see any Germans anymore in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew something must happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the jeep arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told us, you know, that you guys going to be free now, you know, and the American army is just behind us, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They should be here pretty soon, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everything will be fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we really know how-- really felt at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was our freedom, we call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that people couldn't even really dance or-- we were so weak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in our heart, we felt, you know, that something is really happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
